at all.}) (9. f3 {Does not change much after:} c5) (9. Bg5 c5 {[%csl Gd4] The
most natural response.} ({Probably also playable is:} 9... h6 10. Bd2 Nd7) 10.
Qd2 Bd7 11. f3 Qe8 12. Kh1 h5 $13 {[%cal Gf6h7] Black has an excellent
position.}) (9. Nb5 {[%csl Rd4] Trying immediately to exchange the strong
